04:41.000 --> 04:44.000
Of your boys who've gone on to study later,

04:44.000 --> 04:47.000
how have they done that without a school qualification?

04:47.000 --> 04:53.000
For Joel, who's the eldest, he kind of got a bit bored

04:53.000 --> 04:58.000
here at the age of 13 decided he'd like to find something outside of the home to do.

04:58.000 --> 05:03.000
So we applied for him for the next year to do a computing course

05:03.000 --> 05:07.000
