05:11.000 --> 05:14.000
then went on to do another course, eventually went through

05:14.000 --> 05:20.000
and finished university younger than any other university student in Bendigo.

05:20.000 --> 05:24.000
We can't let children just pick and choose what they want to eat

05:24.000 --> 05:28.000
